<ab facs="#facs_186_r2l27"><expan>bürge<ex>n</ex></expan> gemant nach <expan>auſweıſu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> ſchuldbrıefs Vnd </ab>
